=head1 DESCRIPTION

Contains the details for an SFTP connector connection.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 HostKey => Str

The SSH public key of the remote SFTP server. This is returned during
the initial connection attempt when you call C<TestConnection>. It
allows you to retrieve the valid server host key to update the
connector when you are unable to obtain it in advance.



